Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:30.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:38.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Today is Obon so we'll be doing \Na ghost-themed episode
