Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:21.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do I shout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:26.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's so painful that it'll make me \Nshout "OUCH!" all of a sudden?
