Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.52,0:02:59.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't get exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:03.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(515.429,672.286)}We also prepared our best prank right at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,665.428)}so just enjoy the show without worries
