Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.85,Marin,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.85,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Ganbare!! FRESH! Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Good evening everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.80,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.67,Marin,,0,0,0,,The day leader this time-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:10.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'm the Stand Out! Chairperson, \NHidaka Marin of middle school 3rd year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:13.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll be in charge of... of....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:14.67,Marin,,0,0,0,,Of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.70,Kano,,0,0,0,,Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,...being the day leader!\NPlease bear with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.70,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.05,Marin,,0,0,0,,These four are the line-up for today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.62,Marin,,0,0,0,,Please introduce yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.40,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I'm Nonaka Kokona of middle school 1st year!\NPleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:38.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm the Student Council President, \NShintani Yuzumi of middle school 3rd year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yuzumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile so here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.22,Kano,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.87,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kanonon! Kanonon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.85,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Genkina ko! (Cheerful girl!)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm the Performance Chairperson,\NFujihira Kano of middle school 2nd year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:08.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we had the Art Open Class yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's been awhile since we had an open class
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.25,Kano,,0,0,0,,It really has been and I enjoyed it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Since orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:17.55,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's art, you know... Art
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,It was really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,It was like "Art is an explosion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.77,Marin,,0,0,0,,We played around a lot in second period
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,How was the third period?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.70,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The third period is... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'd say that it was very unique
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,It was Yuzumi and the elementary schoolers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,Ohh, it's the first period
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:40.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The paintings at the back are quite something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,They drew portrait of themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:44.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Looks great
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, none of them are here today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:46.57,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Only second and third period members
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The one with twintail
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.60,Kano,,0,0,0,,Twintail and pink scarf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,They look similar in appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.75,Kano,,0,0,0,,They do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,All of them wore pink scarf
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.47,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Kawaii
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.70,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,How was the second period?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:06.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,Right at the end of the second period\Nwhen we were doing live painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.00,Marin,,0,0,0,,I splashed the paint around quite a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:12.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,and ended up making a bit of a mess out of it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:16.85,Marin,,0,0,0,,Because of that, I got scolded yesterday and even today by the teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's fine, you were just 'standing out'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:21.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,You got paint around here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,Around there, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,Some even got on our hair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:27.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,and our face too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,It was pretty tough but it was really fun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:37.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,To move around this much in an open class is a first for me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:41.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Even though this is the third art open class event,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.35,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,it's a fresh experience for me since it's my first
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,This picture is... something else
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Third period!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.67,Kano,,0,0,0,,Seeing Yuzumi and the elementary schoolers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.42,Marin,,0,0,0,,Miku's face looks quite surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:59.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,In the third period, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Well... Lately, I'm often seen as an elementary schooler
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was often told that I'm like an elementary schooler
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.40,Marin,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, you're a senior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I was told that a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Now, now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it means you're youthful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:18.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,Well then, now's a good time to call Mori-sensei out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:19.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.77,Marin,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.90,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Mori-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here I go everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Mori-sen! Mori-sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:30.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,A guy with back pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:32.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:32.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Mori-sen! Mori-sen! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:37.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I do get back pain once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:41.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's probably because of the open class
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,and I was a bit too festive during Gekidan Prestage's final show after-party
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:47.20,T/N,,0,0,0,,[T/N: Mori-sensei was the scriptwriter for Gekidan Prestage's play this year]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Lots of things happened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.20,Kano,,0,0,0,,The heck you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I let out a groan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's a ticking time bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, from art class yesterday... Can you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:01.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's pink here because of Hidaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Hidaka~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:06.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you all got your overalls dirty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:10.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But this is my one and only vest and it is now stained with paint
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:14.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Later- It's not something to yay about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.27,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.80,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The paint won't come off our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, you did use your bare hands to paint after all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:26.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But in the end, there wasn't improvement in your drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:27.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:31.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Marin wrote "Yuzumi" just now
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.90,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,But she got the "zu" wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even though you're in the same grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,She wrote "su"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:40.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kano pointed it out, but she was like "It's fine~"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:42.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone! Take a seat- \NOh wait, no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's day leader duty. Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright then, day leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:53.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,Please treat us well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:07.10,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Don't you think...the line-up feels peculiar this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It just somehow felt like that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:14.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It feels great, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:16.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The air feels strange right from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:22.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it somehow felt like you were putting up a brave front
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's what we'll be doing in the first period
Comment: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:30.77,Topics,,0,0,0,,First Period
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:30.77,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fscx110\fscy150\pos(631.619,674.857)}FRESH{\i1}!{\i0} Monday Supernatural Entities Quiz~{\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640.143,586.571)}Fresh! Monday Supernatural Entities Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:37.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Perhaps because you all knew that it's gonna be somewhat related to ghost,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I feel like you were forcing yourself to be excited
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you bad with these, Shintani and Fujihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm super bad with these
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I know that your reactions will be great
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How about you, Nonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:55.77,Kokona,,0,0,0,,If Kano-chan and Yuzumin starts crying, \NI might ended up getting scared too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:59.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,If they break down in tears, you'll join them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Let's cry together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:05.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shintani seems like she gets scared living in dorm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I really can't stand these
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:12.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,She checks every parts of her room \Nlike the toilet and under her bed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:14.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Stop it Marin! Don't tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What did you check for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.55,Kano,,0,0,0,,She's so scared
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be bad if something's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It would!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,The space under the bad is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:27.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sorry to tell you this but this is a true story
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.60,Kano,,0,0,0,,Stop it! That's enough
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,There are lots of "things" in that dorm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,STOOOOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:35.45,Kano,,0,0,0,,No! Just no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm currently living in a single room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hold it! I shouldn't be laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But it's so fun right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm honestly scared~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.70,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:49.87,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's really scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:50.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,During shower as well
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.65,Kano,,0,0,0,,Really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,While using shampoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.25,Kano,,0,0,0,,Or when washing my face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm like "I know you're there..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:10:58.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:00.27,Marin,,0,0,0,,My head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's up with you! You're also acting a bit weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're not afraid of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,I love yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:14.25,T/N,,0,0,0,,[T/N: Yokai is a broad term that encompasses various supernatural beings so I'll leave it untranslated]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:09.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You love them huh? But that makes you more sensitive-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The heck is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Were you scared for real just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.27,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm seriously scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind. Let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.10,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:31.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll now have you challenge a quiz on supernatural entities
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:36.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It is said that psychic phenonemon \Nare prone to occur during obon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,and this is how the quiz related to that will be like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:46.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,They are divided into different categories and points
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:46.24,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9950ED&\fscx138\fscy118\pos(408,188.571)}Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:46.24,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9950ED&\pos(644.572,189.714)\fscx141\fscy126}Yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:46.24,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9950ED&\pos(910.858,188.571)\fscx120\fscy124}Drawings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:49.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,and you'll each have the option to choose one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:54.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,For instance, if you choose Spirit 10 points, it'll be a somewhat easy question for Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:12:00.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Same with Drawings. The question gets increasingly harder for higher points
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:06.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So take that into consideration and then make your choice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So, who wanna go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:12.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shintani who is the most fearful can go first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're even scared to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then... Drawings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:20.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How much points?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,20!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:29.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The Big Three Yokai of Japan are Kappa, Tengu and the last one is? Please draw your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ready... Start!
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.55,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Drawings??
Comment: 0,0:12:30.94,0:15:59.41,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,Quiz 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:15:59.41,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H475E2D&\c&HE1B22B&\fscx100\fscy110\pos(541.714,568.714)}Drawings Quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:15:59.41,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H475E2D&\c&HE36BE9&\fscx120\fscy110\pos(837.857,570.571)}20 Points
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:15:59.41,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H475E2D&\fscx90\fscy90\pos(694,627.714)}The Big Three Yokai of Japan are Kappa, Tengu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:15:59.41,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H475E2D&\fscx101\fscy86\pos(699,676.667)}and the last one is? Please draw your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, since we just had an art class!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The theme of your drawing is "Dynamism"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:39.95,T/N,,0,0,0,,[T/N: Mori-sensei is referencing the theme from the Art Open Class]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,What was it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:40.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Inner eye
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do you even remember? \NWhat did you learn, Nonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.67,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I learned about "Concept"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The term "Concept", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Inner eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was taught in the third period
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What kind of teaching was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:55.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Mechanism?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:58.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,No, it's not! It's cubism!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's cubism!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:02.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you watching this, Yamashita-sensei? They've already forgotten it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You learned cubism but you said mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,20 points question
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Kappa, Tengu and what's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:16.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's quite famous
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Just draw something
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:22.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Maybe It'll be correct
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:27.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't stop, keep thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It is one of the major yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,A scary one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:41.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka is fast! Your drawing is looking good
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:41.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,Done
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Done? In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you just completely done with this quiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:49.75,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm done...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Wanna have a go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:52.42,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at Fujihira's answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Ta dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Kappa, Tengu and?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sadako
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How modern!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.47,Kano,,0,0,0,,Modern!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But yeah, it is quite a major one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Your depiction of Sadako is surprisingly good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.17,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes, her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hair coming out of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Were you scared from just drawing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:15.70,Kano,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:18.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Seriously. Like, really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:21.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even just by saying her name too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sadako is that-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.95,Kano,,0,0,0,,This mood right now is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:27.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and if you say "Sadako", she'll come for you
