Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,Ahh! That scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:34.87,Kano,,0,0,0,,Nothing
