Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I don't know the name
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Just show your answer first. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(901.714,312.286)}Yamamba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(914.285,193.429)}Yamamba!
