Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yamamba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:56.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's not Namahage, but instead Yamamba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. It is indeed scary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yamamba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:06.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It does have some dynamism to it especially the hair
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, next one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ohh, that looks artistic
