Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, reveal your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.65,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Hitotsume-kozo (One-eyed monster)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It looks lot like Medama no Oyaji \N{\i1}(character from GeGeGe no Kitaro){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.55,Marin,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,He seems like he'll say "Hey Kitaro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,I love Kitaro~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You drew it well with a cloak and all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.57,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Does it wear cloak?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's highly unlikely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:36.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why would a Japanese monster wear western clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it could be wearing furoshiki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:39.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But it does look good
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Lastly, Hidaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Show it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:45.92,Marin,,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.47,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's Karakasa-obake
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:49.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That got dull rather quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Kappa, Tengu and suddenly, Karakasa-Obake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:54.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The last yokai is so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But you did drew it well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.00,Marin,,0,0,0,,I love it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, here's the correct answer!
Comment: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:12.54,Topics,,0,0,0,,Quiz 1 Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:12.54,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H475E2D&\c&H1010E8&\fscx170\fscy250\pos(651.429,663.286)\3a&H00&}Answer: Oni (Ogre/Troll)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's Oni!
