Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It is also a yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So, Fujihira- wait no. \NShintani's answer could be correct at first
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Oni! Oni! Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,No, it's not! That's Yamamba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:12.90,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You said it was Yamamba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:14.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:17.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, no one answered correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:18.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, moving on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You can pick the next one, Nonaka
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Spirit, Yokai or Drawings. Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,20 points under Yokai
