Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:41.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is one of the major yokai as well, and it's worth 20 points
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.22,Kano,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows this
