Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,Do we just write the answer down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:45.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, though it is also okay to draw
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But you can just write them to save time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Show your answers at once
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is a easy-peasy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Oh you guys can even draw it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:01.70,Kano,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,No, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.67,Marin,,0,0,0,,In anime
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:04.95,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,In anime, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,They say it often appears in Harajuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.72,Kano,,0,0,0,,That's what I hate about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,That's such an old man thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.17,Kano,,0,0,0,,You're purposely scaring us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,There's none in Harajuku! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I got carried away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But it is there in the dorm
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,OH COME ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:25.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I SERIOUSLY HATE YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize later. But even so, it's there
