Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:35.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Okay, starting from Hidaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:42.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,A woman with a long, growing neck
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.95,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Its neck can grow (long)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next, Shintani
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.85,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Its neck can grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next, Fujihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,Its neck can grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, here's the correct answer
Comment: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.31,Topics,,0,0,0,,Quiz 2 Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.31,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\3c&H475E2D&\c&H1010E8&\fscx150\fscy230\pos(644.571,649.572)\3a&H00&}Answer: Its neck can grow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:01.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's neck can grow. Everyone answered correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.47,Kano,,0,0,0,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:13.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Even my backpain is going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:19.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're looking really scary there, Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:23.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You can choose next, Fujihira
