Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ohh you've done it now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:36.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The leading ghost story teller has countless first-hand experience with psychic phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:40.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,and has moustache as his trademark look. Who is he?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Write it down. He's quite famous
