Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:21:12.81,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H475E2D&\fscx80\fscy90\pos(640,673.429)\3a&H00&}psychic phenomena and has moustache as his trademark look. Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Moustache is his trademark
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:52.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,People often do impression of him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:53.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:58.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,He used to be a "reaction {\i1}geinin {\i0} (entertainer)" during our times long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,He was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,He has such a wide range of talent
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:06.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So... No idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:07.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Then, Shintani
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.15,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I only know his first name
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,First name only? Alright, let's see it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.20,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Jirou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Jirou-san huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How does he tell his ghost story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:21.20,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,He's like "It's scary... It's scary..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:23.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's Jirou-san huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.70,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Ehh? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:30.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Calm down Shintani! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:35.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Is that how Jirou-san looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,His trademark moustache isn't even there
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira seems like she's done
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:44.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka can't stop drawing. She's really into it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Done, Fujihira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, show it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.65,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's Hiiiii~Muuuuu~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:56.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but the question is asking about {\i1}who{\i0}  the person is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's Hiimuu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hiimuu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:05.42,Kano,,0,0,0,,He has moustache and ghost are like "Muuuuu~" in ghost song, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ghost song?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.85,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,It goes like "Muuuuu~"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:10.82,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:13.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all! Hiimuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:13.97,Kano,,0,0,0,,Hiimuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:16.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hiimuu huh? How does he speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Like that huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, next person!
