Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:34.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's Gushiken Jirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:34.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It could be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It might be Gushiken Jirou
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:39.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Combine the two names
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:41.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,The guy with the curly hair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:46.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That curly-haired guy is known for telling scary stories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next, Nonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:52.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at her answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.65,Kokona,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Read it please
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kaidou Jirou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Kaidou Jirou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:04.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It could be Jirou-san and either Gushiken or Kaidou as his last name
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It could also be Hiimuu Jirou-san
