Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It "J", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:20.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was imagining him in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:22.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, can you do an impression of him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,"It's scary... It's scary..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Only the "Ji" of Junji came to mind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.50,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:31.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Gushiken-san is a former professional boxer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.92,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he come to mind when talking about moustache?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.60,0:21:36.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's true but he doesn't tell ghost story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:38.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,He seems likely to do so
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the last question!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:45.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You can choose the last one, Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.05,Marin,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,30 points under Yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:58.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What do you call the Yokai parade that begins in the dead of night when people are sound asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Start writing your answer now
