Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:25:34.61,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H475E2D&\fscx90\fscy93\3a&H00&\pos(674.286,626.571)}What do you call the Yokai parade that begins
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:25:34.61,Topics (Thin Outline),,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\3c&H475E2D&\fscx90\fscy93\3a&H00&\pos(673.144,676.858)}in the dead of night when people are sound asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:01.82,Kano,,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.82,Kano,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is probably the hardest question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:10.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even I couldn't think of the answer right away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It may be difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:23.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a term that sometimes comes up in the ghost story that children reads
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:27.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hint, it's made up of four kanji characters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:29.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Mine's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:32.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hidaka doesn't seem like she could only write four kanji
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.82,0:22:34.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You got this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.32,0:22:36.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,So it's made up of four kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that it's not as well. Believe in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.77,0:22:42.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You've already wrote your answer after all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:46.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is the parade called?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:50.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:53.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:55.00,T/N,,0,0,0,,[T/N: Poor Mori-sensei. Marin didn't pick up the cue. lol]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:55.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:57.85,Marin,,0,0,0,,You can move just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:00.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:04.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's extremely painful if I bend my back this way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:06.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:12.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What do you call the Yokai parade that begins in the dead of night when people are sound asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:13.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Wanna have a go, Fujihira?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:14.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:15.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Show your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:17.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sleep paralysis
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:18.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sleep paralysis huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.90,0:23:22.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So they're doing the parade while also making you unable to move huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:26.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's a rather interesting drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:29.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How are the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:30.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyone done?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:33.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:35.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Think harder Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:39.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You seem knowledgeable in this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.22,0:23:40.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I don't know the kanji
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:42.82,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's what
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.10,0:23:47.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,Ehh? Gimme a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:48.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:53.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka has once again included a drawing. \NLet's have a look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:54.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Done?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:55.20,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:57.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's see it! Show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:01.30,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Jinyokoushin (lit: PeopleNightParade)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:04.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It does sound like it could be that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:05.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,Exactly as it is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:10.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The Yokai parade that begins in the dead of night when people are asleep, or in short, PeopleNightParade huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:14.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You just cut most of the words out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:17.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't you laugh at it, sleep paralysis girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:20.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you done, Shintani?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright, show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:25.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Reigun Mikkai (lit: SpiritArmySecretMeeting)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:27.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That seems likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.87,0:24:29.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.50,0:24:32.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sounds possible, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.00,0:24:37.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It was hit or miss but it's still a very educated guess
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.12,0:24:34.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.27,0:24:39.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sounds possible... Maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.45,0:24:42.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Finalize yours too, Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.45,0:24:47.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What have you been looking at??
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:48.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.87,0:24:50.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.80,0:24:52.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm scared for my back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.92,0:24:54.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Super scary
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.07,0:24:54.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.85,0:24:58.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Even in dorms, I'm scared for my back so I'm always leaning against the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.95,0:24:57.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.90,0:25:00.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,The mirror is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.10,0:25:02.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Afraid that something could be behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.47,0:25:03.42,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's why I'd touch my back
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.42,0:25:04.37,Kano,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.37,0:25:05.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What do you mean??
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.25,0:25:08.17,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Like this! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.42,0:25:11.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So, if {\i1}"something"{\i0}  were to hug you-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:14.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Please stop! For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.00,0:25:17.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I wasn't even trying to scare you at all just now
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.12,0:25:20.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, let's take a look at Hidaka's answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.65,0:25:24.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hidamashii Youyuku (lit: FlamingSpiritsMovement)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.87,0:25:26.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The heck is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.17,0:25:29.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,FlamingSpiritsMovement participated by Yokai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.72,0:25:32.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.52,0:25:34.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's the correct answer!
Comment: 0,0:25:34.61,0:25:50.77,Topics,,0,0,0,,Quiz 4 Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.61,0:25:50.77,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)\3c&H475E2D&\c&H1010E8&\fscx115\fscy180\3a&H00&\pos(640,644.572)}Answer: Hyakki Yakou (Night Parade of 100 Demons)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.75,0:25:36.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's Hyakki Yakou
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.90,0:25:39.37,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.67,0:25:39.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.50,0:25:44.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,If you don't remember this, they'll come for you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.87,0:25:42.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.35,0:25:45.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,I have to make a note
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.52,0:25:48.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But you can't take this back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.35,0:25:49.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'll tear the notes off
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.70,0:25:53.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, since everyone has 20 points,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.12,0:25:55.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.10,0:25:59.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The only thing that you guys knew were Rokurokubi
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.97,0:26:01.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Is it over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.02,0:26:02.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.65,0:26:05.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The final result is a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.65,0:26:08.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's the end of the first period!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.60,0:26:11.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the break time everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.65,0:26:12.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.25,0:26:17.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.10,0:26:21.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,Time to read... the postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.10,0:26:22.90,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.90,0:26:23.92,Kano,,0,0,0,,All yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.92,0:26:24.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Shall I?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.65,0:26:27.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.25,0:26:30.17,Marin,,0,0,0,,Such a wonderful mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.17,0:26:31.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.57,0:26:33.65,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,How wonderful~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.40,0:26:35.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'll read 'em now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.72,0:26:36.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.30,0:26:41.42,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Good evening to everyone in Sakura Gakuin, \NMori-sensei and the staff!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.42,0:26:42.67,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.75,0:26:47.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Without further ado, I'll now introduce my annual summer tradition to you. "{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.55,0:26:53.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"My friend who is a fukei living in Tokyo goes on a trip to my hometown, Hokkaido..."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.22,0:26:56.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"...during summer holiday to do some mountain climbing."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.60,0:26:57.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.02,0:27:02.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Once we reached the top, we enjoyed the view while listening to Sakura Gakuin songs."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.32,0:27:04.50,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Thank you~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.65,0:27:08.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Listening to MagiMelo while in the midst of the grand nature is the best."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.00,0:27:10.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,Magic Melody... Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.30,0:27:14.27,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Have you ever went to Hokkaido before?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:17.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Although it's still hot, please do your best during lesson!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.70,0:27:18.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,From Asariba
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:21.67,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.35,0:27:24.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kano wants to go to Hokkaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.35,0:27:25.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.97,0:27:27.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.80,0:27:28.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:29.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.60,0:27:31.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's vast
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.25,0:27:32.40,Marin,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat the Hotate (scallop) there
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.52,0:27:33.42,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.42,0:27:35.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Who here has climbed a mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.47,0:27:36.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.42,0:27:37.82,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.02,0:27:42.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,We went mountain climbing for training camp every year in my elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.72,0:27:43.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Really? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.92,0:27:47.42,Marin,,0,0,0,,We climbed non-stop for like five hours
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.42,0:27:48.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,It was really fun
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.50,0:27:49.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Wow~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.62,0:27:50.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.77,0:27:53.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,It was so exhausting during climbing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.72,0:27:55.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,But there's a technique for mountaineering
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.50,0:28:01.05,Marin,,0,0,0,,Always keep the gap between your steps the same
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.05,0:28:02.55,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,You said it before
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.55,0:28:05.65,Marin,,0,0,0,,If you do that, you won't get tired as easily
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.65,0:28:11.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,And also, if you keep a steady continuous pace, you won't get tired at all
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.82,0:28:15.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,A mountaineering expert taught me that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.67,0:28:15.87,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Really? Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.87,0:28:17.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.57,0:28:19.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's true that the climbing is a struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.90,0:28:24.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,but the moment you reached the top and see this scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.37,0:28:24.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:29.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,it makes you want to climb the mountain all over again
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.32,0:28:31.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,You won't understand unless you climb huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:31.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.07,0:28:33.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,I wanna climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.35,0:28:35.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,It feels like you're on top of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.70,0:28:37.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.40,0:28:39.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.20,0:28:43.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that they listen to Sakura Gakuin songs on top of the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.00,0:28:44.65,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,I know right?
