Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.32,0:29:12.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I don't really have any summer break but I go surfing in summer every year."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:13.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Amazing
