Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.67,0:29:34.35,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Kawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.35,0:29:36.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm not Aritomoto
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:38.25,Marin,,0,0,0,,Marine sports huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.25,0:29:40.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,Kano wants to go surfing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.35,0:29:41.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.20,0:29:43.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna try it even though it seems hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:45.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I wanna try riding on a banana boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.32,0:29:48.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.62,0:29:49.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely fall
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:51.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Right? We'll lose balance
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.52,0:29:56.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,I wanna try out the water jetpack that makes you fly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.20,0:29:57.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The one that makes you hover?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.77,0:30:00.92,Kano,,0,0,0,,I want! Good balancing skill seems essential for it though
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.25,0:30:02.75,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I wanna go surfing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.95,0:30:06.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,I know right! Same with me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.37,0:30:07.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Ride the wave
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.60,0:30:09.37,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Right? I wanna go to the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.07,0:30:11.52,Kano,,0,0,0,,I wanna go with everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.52,0:30:12.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Everyone in SG
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.47,0:30:16.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Let's work even harder and then request the teacher to let us go there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.82,0:30:17.72,Kano,,0,0,0,,Request!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.72,0:30:19.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,"We wanna go to the beach!"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.82,0:30:19.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Please~
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.37,0:30:23.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thank you Toki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.75,0:30:27.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So many dreams for summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.62,0:30:30.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And yet they always end up unfulfilled though
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.42,0:30:36.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now that you're the president, you should take command and organize a strike or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.10,0:30:42.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Be like "We won't practice unless you fulfill them!"
Dialogue: 1,0:30:42.32,0:30:44.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright! Moving on to the second period!
Comment: 0,0:30:44.31,0:30:49.37,Topics,,0,0,0,,Second Period
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.31,0:30:49.37,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\fscx120\fscy160\pos(662.476,688.571)}FRESH{\i1}!{\i0} Monday, Ghost Storytelling in Midsummer {\i1}!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.77,0:30:49.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,599.143)}FRESH! Monday, Ghost Storytelling in Midsummer!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.05,0:30:52.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is where we get down to today's main topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.27,0:30:54.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You'll be reading some ghost stories
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:58.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Being skillful at this is also crucial to becoming a Super Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.47,0:31:03.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So do your best to frighten the viewers with your storytelling
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.87,0:31:08.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,For this, you'll be in a group of two
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:11.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,and read your story together
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.20,0:31:19.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Both groups are clueless about the other's story so there's a possibility that you'd be scared by it as well
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.25,0:31:21.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How will the team be divided?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.75,0:31:24.97,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Marin-chan and me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.75,0:31:24.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,Kokona and me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.97,0:31:28.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So Nonaka and Hidaka, \Nand Shintani and Fujihira
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.67,0:31:30.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you two gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:34.27,Kano,,0,0,0,,No, we won't! We're always scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.27,0:31:36.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You even get scared from reading it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.17,0:31:37.67,Kano,,0,0,0,,Really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.67,0:31:39.17,Marin,,0,0,0,,There's candle now...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.17,0:31:41.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why? Something wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.90,0:31:43.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you scared, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.15,0:31:44.40,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.82,0:31:46.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling well today
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.35,0:31:49.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The fact that Marin is not feeling well is scary
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.60,0:31:50.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's a sign, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.37,0:31:52.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The heck is happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.92,0:31:55.17,Kano,,0,0,0,,I really hate this! I can't! I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.45,0:31:58.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Was that a pr- \NOh well, whatever. Let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.32,0:32:02.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Who'll go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.95,0:32:08.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll start with team Hidaka and Nonaka first
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.50,0:32:10.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ready... Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.50,0:32:13.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Wait! Will it stay like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.27,0:32:14.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.30,0:32:15.50,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.92,0:32:17.05,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Okay, nevermind
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.42,0:32:22.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's your groan that's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.85,0:32:24.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Let's move over there a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.65,0:32:23.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.92,0:32:27.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kano doesn't like the gap here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.15,0:32:28.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'll follow
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.75,0:32:29.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.10,0:32:31.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:32.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.82,0:32:33.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.17,0:32:35.45,Marin,,0,0,0,,"Present"
Comment: 0,0:32:36.74,0:38:28.41,Topics,,0,0,0,,Second Period, First Story
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.74,0:38:28.41,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H7F11DE&\3c&HECEBEC&\3a&H0E&\fscx140\fscy116\bord60\clip(m 965 630 l 965 629 966 628 966 631 b 964 626 971 617 980 620 l 1237 620 b 1244 619 1250 624 1250 631 l 1250 680 b 1251 688 1246 692 1240 694 l 979 694 b 972 695 965 692 964 682)\pos(1110.286,685.143)}PRESENT
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.80,0:32:40.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,This is a true story
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.85,0:32:45.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san who is an office worker at a neighbouring company
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.87,0:32:51.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,has been harassed by a stalker since around a week ago
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.77,0:32:56.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,As for the harassment...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.65,0:33:02.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,She finds weird things inside her mail box every morning
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.77,0:33:06.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,First, a shoelace
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.35,0:33:09.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Next, a belt buckle
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.97,0:33:12.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,The next one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.07,0:33:15.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,a shirt button
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.65,0:33:19.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,Then, on the next day, there was a beanie inside it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.70,0:33:25.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,However, because there hasn't been anything else since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.72,0:33:31.05,Kokona,,0,0,0,,EIko-san didn't inform the police despite feeling eerie about it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.85,0:33:34.95,Kokona,,0,0,0,,On a morning a few days after the last incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:40.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,while thinking {\i1}"What on earth was all those about anyway"{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.97,0:33:44.90,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san went to her mail box to pick up the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.02,0:33:51.75,Kokona,,0,0,0,,As she opened her mail box, she found a letter instead of a newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:54.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,The content are as follows
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.72,0:33:58.47,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sorry to have kept you waiting for so long."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.55,0:34:04.12,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I gave you presents that represent my feelings starting from my feet."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.82,0:34:07.25,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But, before long, I reached my head already."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.25,0:34:10.22,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I thought about what I should do next."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.52,0:34:14.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A good idea came to me though it took me quite awhile."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.65,0:34:19.55,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Look forward to it from tomorrow onwards."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.90,0:34:23.67,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san immediately dropped to the floor in terror
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.20,0:34:28.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It must be him..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.90,0:34:35.80,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was scared to stay at home that day so she stayed overnight at a friend's house
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.52,0:34:42.40,Kokona,,0,0,0,,On the next morning, Eiko-san went back to her home for a change of clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.00,0:34:46.75,Kokona,,0,0,0,,She wondered about what might be inside her mail box
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.75,0:34:51.52,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Despite the fear, she opened it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.67,0:34:55.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,What she found inside was...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.10,0:34:57.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,a bloodied toenail
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.35,0:35:04.77,Marin,,0,0,0,,Next to it was another letter
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.02,0:35:09.25,Marin,,0,0,0,,The letter reads as follows
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.60,0:35:15.17,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"After my clothes, I'll now be giving you parts of my body from the bottom up."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.90,0:35:19.85,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Oh! But it would be bad if you stay at your friend's house."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.15,0:35:23.00,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Cause I like visiting you when you're sleeping at home."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.67,0:35:28.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"If you sleep at your friend's house again, I might do the same things to her."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.60,0:35:32.12,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Telling the police won't change a thing as well"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.75,0:35:35.35,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Look forward to tomorrow as well, okay?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.65,0:35:40.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san trembled in fear and felt completely helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.07,0:35:43.92,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I can't escape him anymore"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.35,0:35:47.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san took a leave from work
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.92,0:35:51.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,and shut herself in her home for hours on end
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.35,0:35:59.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,Unable to sleep... All she did was tremble in fear at the corner of her room
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.10,0:36:06.42,Marin,,0,0,0,,And of course, she couldn't check her mail box
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.17,0:36:12.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then, on a morning several days later, her front door bell rang
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.27,0:36:25.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I've been on leave for days so it could be someone from work who's worried about me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.95,0:36:27.80,Marin,,0,0,0,,Thinking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.25,0:36:32.52,Marin,,0,0,0,,She went to open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.52,0:36:34.75,Marin,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.65,0:36:37.60,Marin,,0,0,0,,There was no one outside
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.87,0:36:44.05,Marin,,0,0,0,,Then, as she was about to close the door
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.37,0:36:48.12,Marin,,0,0,0,,The things that caught her eyes were
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.12,0:36:52.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,Fingernails scattered on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.77,0:36:54.12,Marin,,0,0,0,,Hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.67,0:36:55.95,Marin,,0,0,0,,And lastly...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.67,0:36:58.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eyeballs
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.77,0:37:15.15,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san's phone rang
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.37,0:37:19.07,Marin,,0,0,0,,She fearfully answered it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.55,0:37:23.57,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Why didn't you accept my presents?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.35,0:37:28.32,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I prepared lots of them for you, \Nand yet, you accepted none."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.62,0:37:33.40,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Ohh I see! You're already satisfied with all the presents, right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.87,0:37:36.77,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"If so, why don't you give me your presents then?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.85,0:37:39.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san threw away the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.50,0:37:42.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,and ran outside barefooted
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.00,0:37:50.50,Marin,,0,0,0,,However, Eiko-san became exhausted after not eating for days since leaving her home
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.02,0:37:54.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,She became unable to move right then and there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.65,0:37:58.15,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What kind of present will you give me?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.20,0:38:06.75,Marin,,0,0,0,,She turned around and a bloodied man who is without his hair, fingernails and both his eyes was standing there
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:13.97,Kokona,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Since I gave you that many presents, it's fine if I ask you to give me what I want, right?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.37,0:38:16.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\}KYAAAAAAAAAAHHH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.92,0:38:16.35,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\}KYAAAAAAAAAAHHH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.92,0:38:26.55,Kokona,,0,0,0,,After that, Eiko-san's whereabouts became \Nunknown and she remains missing to this day
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.35,0:38:42.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Wait... Can you zoom in on Shintani-san's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.95,0:38:46.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.80,0:38:50.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What... What kind of expression is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.05,0:38:53.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were the most frightened
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.17,0:38:56.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.45,0:38:58.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It was really good, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.05,0:39:03.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This is a segment where you try to scare others after all
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.67,0:39:06.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Seriously, what's wrong with you Shintani??
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.92,0:39:09.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.75,0:39:12.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She only screamed because it's written there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.32,0:39:16.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\fs120\bord10}I CAN'T STAND THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:19.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.35,0:39:22.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.72,0:39:27.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm not really frightened by this. \NIt's the dorm that I'm scared of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.60,0:39:28.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Dorm??
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.47,0:39:29.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.15,0:39:34.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,What should I do if that person comes to our dorm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.32,0:39:37.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! You're well-protected
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:39.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,He won't come to your dorm
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.47,0:39:40.32,Kano,,0,0,0,,He will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.32,0:39:42.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.05,0:39:44.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.40,0:39:46.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.80,0:39:48.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.17,0:39:49.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.62,0:39:51.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.17,0:39:55.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka was great just now, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.40,0:39:57.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Her expression for example
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.07,0:39:58.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.05,0:40:03.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Hidaka was talking the whole time in the dressing room
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.35,0:40:02.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.40,0:40:05.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Who was she talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.42,0:40:07.10,Marin,,0,0,0,,She's talking to herself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.47,0:40:12.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Can you stop acting so scary? \NWe'll honestly get scared if you continue
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.50,0:40:13.20,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.20,0:40:15.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're doing it to the wrong bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.82,0:40:16.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.27,0:40:21.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next up! It's Shintani's and Fujihira's turn
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.52,0:40:22.85,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, we're just reading them. It's not scary at all
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.25,0:40:22.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.85,0:40:26.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That scream just now was so unexpected, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.17,0:40:28.15,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That's the scariest part!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.15,0:40:29.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The story wasn't as scary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.57,0:40:31.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's the scream that gets you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.07,0:40:34.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Did you improvise that or was it written?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.82,0:40:35.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's written
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.87,0:40:39.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You deserve a perfect mark for reenacting the scream
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.77,0:40:39.57,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.57,0:40:41.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating but you have to agree
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.80,0:40:41.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.95,0:40:43.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.70,0:40:46.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You're really amusing, Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.90,0:40:50.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even us got scared after reading the story
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.40,0:40:52.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The story choice is a bit too scary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:54.95,Kano,,0,0,0,,I'm always called for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.22,0:40:56.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.07,0:40:58.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.40,0:40:59.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I wonder why
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.40,0:41:00.52,Kano,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.87,0:41:02.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,Every single time!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.87,0:41:02.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.95,0:41:06.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Here's Shintani and Fujihira reading their ghost story
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.50,0:41:07.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.70,0:41:18.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,At a certain junior high school, there was a ghost story that had been circulating since long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.60,0:41:24.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It was rumored that if you go to the music room at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.47,0:41:29.62,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,the ghost of a woman who committed suicide will appear
Dialogue: 1,0:41:30.90,0:41:39.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,This is a story of Eiko-san, a student who went to that school and had actually experienced it
Comment: 0,0:41:34.94,0:46:25.64,Topics,,0,0,0,,Second Period, Second Story
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.94,0:46:25.64,Topics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\c&H7F11DE&\3c&HECEBEC&\3a&H0C&\fscx65\fscy100\bord60\clip(m 966 633 b 966 624 972 617 981 620 l 1238 620 b 1243 620 1251 623 1250 632 l 1250 681 b 1249 688 1245 695 1239 694 l 981 694 b 973 697 965 690 966 682)\pos(1109.714,681.142)}Music Room at Night
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.65,0:41:45.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It happened in the middle of the final exam period of the second semester
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.72,0:41:51.42,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was doing some last minute cramming for the exam
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.42,0:41:54.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,When the night comes, she realizes something
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.27,0:41:58.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"There's an exam tomorrow."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.30,0:42:04.87,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But I don't have my Science textbook with me. I'd fail my paper at this rate."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.45,0:42:11.55,Kano,,0,0,0,,And so, she decided to go to the school at night to get her textbook back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.40,0:42:16.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,She arrived at the school's guard post
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.05,0:42:20.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,However, there was no one there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.72,0:42:24.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'll run out of time to study if I don't hurry!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.52,0:42:30.47,Kano,,0,0,0,,Thinking that, she decided to sneak into the school
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.50,0:42:36.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san walked cautiously through the dark hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.32,0:42:45.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Despite the eerie feeling in the air, she climbed the stairs and found her way to her classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.37,0:42:54.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She went inside and found her textbook in her locker
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.20,0:42:58.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Phew! Thank god!"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.62,0:43:02.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I have to hurry back home and study."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.70,0:43:11.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Just as Eiko-san was leaving the classrom while saying that, something happened
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.00,0:43:18.97,Kano,,0,0,0,,She could hear the sound of piano coming from the music room
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.52,0:43:22.42,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Who could it be, this late at night?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.90,0:43:28.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san became curious and couldn't hold herself back
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.85,0:43:33.05,Kano,,0,0,0,,She made her way to the music room one step at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.42,0:43:41.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,As she gets closer to the music room, the piano sound steadily gets louder
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.62,0:43:39.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(888,324.857)}Whatchu want??
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.32,0:43:45.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"There must be someone there!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.77,0:43:51.22,Kano,,0,0,0,,She plucked up her courage and opened the door
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.35,0:43:57.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,However, there was no one inside
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.00,0:44:01.00,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The piano sound disappeared as well
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.17,0:44:08.90,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I must've misheard it due to the lack of sleep from all the cramming."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.27,0:44:14.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,She told herself that and left the room
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.82,0:44:17.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,However, as soon as she closed the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.20,0:44:24.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She could hear the piano being played again
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.75,0:44:28.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,"Someone's making fun of me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.60,0:44:34.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She hurried back to the music room
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.45,0:44:42.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She then looked in front of the piano and \Naround it but there was no one to be found
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.60,0:44:46.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The keylid was closed as well
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.62,0:44:52.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Unable to comprehend what's happening, \NEiko-san opened the keylid and tried playing them
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.00,0:44:54.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,However, it didn't make any sound
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.85,0:45:00.37,Kano,,0,0,0,,No sound were made no matter how hard she pressed the key
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.35,0:45:05.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,Then, the moment Eiko-san pressed \Nthe keys with both her hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.02,0:45:08.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,{\fs80}KYAAAAAHHHHH!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.45,0:45:13.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,Her hands were caught in between the lid and the keys
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.92,0:45:17.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Blood trickled down from her hands
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.12,0:45:23.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,Unable to move, Eiko-san screamed until she lost her voice
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.30,0:45:29.65,Kano,,0,0,0,,The music room became dead silent
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.10,0:45:35.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then, she heard a voice coming from behind her
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.60,0:45:41.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What are you doing with my piano?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.17,0:45:45.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She nervously turned her head around
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.72,0:45:49.02,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,and there was a woman smeared with blood
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.45,0:45:52.70,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was silenced by fear
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.67,0:45:58.25,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Then, the bloodied woman said this to her
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.32,0:46:06.10,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Since you played my precious piano without my permission, I guess you don't need those fingers anymore, do you?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.67,0:46:14.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Eiko-san was absent from school on the next day
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.00,0:46:17.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.87,0:46:19.87,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,And the days that follows...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.35,0:46:24.17,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She never turned up to school
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.22,0:46:29.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.30,0:46:33.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,There we have it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.42,0:46:36.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Umm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.32,0:46:38.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shintani's scream fell flat though
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.37,0:46:44.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You wanted to return the favor but they didn't really fell for it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.12,0:46:46.15,Kano,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.95,0:46:48.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,At such a crucial part-
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.10,0:46:51.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's first go back to our usual setup
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.50,0:46:52.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,With lights and all
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.65,0:46:54.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now then
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.27,0:46:58.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shall we move forward for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.47,0:47:00.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.47,0:47:05.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's hear your thoughts about this segment
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.52,0:47:08.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Come forward
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.77,0:47:09.50,Kano,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.50,0:47:11.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of Hidaka more than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.45,0:47:12.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Ehh??
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.00,0:47:13.27,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Ehh?? What??
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.32,0:47:17.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's umm... Let's just line up in the middle first
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.72,0:47:23.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the ghost story lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.47,0:47:24.37,Kano,,0,0,0,,She okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.85,0:47:26.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Umm... Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.40,0:47:29.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well uhh.. Alright, understood
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.40,0:47:34.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's your thoughts about this, Nonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.90,0:47:35.67,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.67,0:47:37.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It really was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.85,0:47:40.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Which part scared you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.25,0:47:44.62,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I was still fine during the quiz but the talking alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.62,0:47:47.70,Kokona,,0,0,0,,\NOh! Yuzumi-chan's scream was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.70,0:47:49.05,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.82,0:47:49.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So that scared you after all
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.95,0:47:52.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking glad after hearing just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.55,0:47:53.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm so glad
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.82,0:47:56.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But yeah, both teams were great
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.32,0:48:00.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Did you see Nonaka's expression just now? I guess you didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.12,0:48:01.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.65,0:48:03.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were clinging to each other the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.77,0:48:07.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira kept looking behind while reading
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.72,0:48:07.70,Kano,,0,0,0,,I was really scared
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.70,0:48:09.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It really was scary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.67,0:48:12.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How about you, Shintani?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.12,0:48:13.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.92,0:48:14.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.05,0:48:17.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Which part was scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.00,0:48:22.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's not the story, but rather the thought of it happening in real life that's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.97,0:48:22.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.12,0:48:22.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.95,0:48:25.17,Kano,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when we get back to our dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.25,0:48:28.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yes... Ahh! I won't be able to sleep today!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.12,0:48:31.25,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, since you'll be remembering all these
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.12,0:48:29.00,Kano,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.25,0:48:32.62,Kano,,0,0,0,,I absolutely cannot
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.70,0:48:33.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.35,0:48:36.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What? What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.87,0:48:38.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.92,0:48:41.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:48:41.77,0:48:41.90,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs20\pos(218,667)}(Don't mind me...\NJust hiding here){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.90,0:48:43.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Ehh?? What's this??
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.05,0:48:48.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.25,0:48:50.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Where have you been!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.07,0:48:53.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The heck is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.37,0:48:56.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It's Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.37,0:48:58.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.27,0:49:00.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sadako is here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.52,0:49:03.75,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.70,0:49:06.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.92,0:49:11.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,No! It's not that I was scared! \NI was just worried about Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.12,0:49:12.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were here??
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.25,0:49:16.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I thought you were sick or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.50,0:49:18.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.82,0:49:21.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.07,0:49:23.55,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I wasn't scared! I was worried about Marin!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.55,0:49:25.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were worried huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.47,0:49:26.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.37,0:49:27.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.60,0:49:32.52,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She has been acting strange ever since we were in the dressing room! I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.52,0:49:34.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She got you worried huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.22,0:49:37.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,However... Tell them the truth Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.87,0:49:39.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's all an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.57,0:49:40.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.47,0:49:48.77,Marin,,0,0,0,,I've been acting ever since we were in dressing room today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.22,0:49:51.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She was acting so strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.45,0:49:54.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, let's uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.72,0:49:55.80,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira-san too
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.30,0:49:57.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You okay Shintani?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.35,0:49:59.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.02,0:49:59.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.22,0:50:02.62,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You were worried more than you were scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.20,0:50:01.57,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's all fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.52,0:50:03.90,Marin,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with me
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.20,0:50:05.22,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.22,0:50:10.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,This somehow turned out to be a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.45,0:50:16.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka kept checking on Hidaka \Nwhenever she was acting strange
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.90,0:50:18.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,I was so scared
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.02,0:50:22.60,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Nonaka kept on comforting her the whole time she was looking distressed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.65,0:50:27.45,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I really thought she was sick or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.45,0:50:31.72,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You must be thinking like \N{\i1}"Don't joke around while I'm reading my story!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.72,0:50:34.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"And yet, I had to keep on reading!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.22,0:50:38.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Actually, you know that we started 3 minutes late, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.10,0:50:40.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.65,0:50:41.77,Kano,,0,0,0,,Eh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.90,0:50:43.85,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.57,0:50:45.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Yes, those 3 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.15,0:50:45.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.97,0:50:46.97,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I HATE YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.57,0:50:48.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.70,0:50:52.10,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm glad! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.97,0:50:52.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,While the staff was-
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.77,0:50:58.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,During the 3 minutes, a pre-recorded video of me and Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.65,0:51:02.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,revealing this set-up was broadcasted
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.52,0:51:04.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Flashing a ghost photo on the studio monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.15,0:51:05.47,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I saw it! I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.67,0:51:07.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,A girl's voice can suddenly be heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.70,0:51:09.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Was this played?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.27,0:51:10.72,Kano,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.85,0:51:13.85,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The light flickers when Hidaka says "My head hurts"
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.50,0:51:17.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about her head hurting!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.80,0:51:21.57,Kano,,0,0,0,,Since she kept saying that, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.40,0:51:21.57,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She made you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.27,0:51:24.30,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Her acting was too good then
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.80,0:51:24.90,Kano,,0,0,0,,Too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.25,0:51:31.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fourth, when Hidaka says "My shoulder hurts", Mori-sensei will feel a back pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.55,0:51:33.12,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,That too?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.12,0:51:35.27,Marin,,0,0,0,,I forgot about this
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.62,0:51:39.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I kept my backpain acting going the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.65,0:51:42.05,Kano,,0,0,0,,So that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.05,0:51:47.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I started off with saying that I have \Nbackpain just because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.15,0:51:49.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I've been worried about you since before we started
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.65,0:51:51.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Man! You're so kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.07,0:51:52.72,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I was so worried!!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.72,0:51:54.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.55,0:51:56.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Sorry Shintani!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.22,0:51:59.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,As for the reason why we went with this line-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.82,0:52:03.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,the teachers chose based on who gets scared the most
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.17,0:52:07.30,Kano,,0,0,0,,Seriously! I'm always chosen for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.42,0:52:10.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And it was decided that it'd be the three of you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.67,0:52:16.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,The teachers asked me who among the members get scared the most
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.82,0:52:18.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,And I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.35,0:52:21.50,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So, it's Hidaka's choice of members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.65,0:52:23.32,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.57,0:52:24.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Fujihira is the main choice every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.05,0:52:26.02,Kano,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Yeah...){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.02,0:52:29.60,Kano,,0,0,0,,It's always me that had to sit near the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.00,0:52:31.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,I really hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.37,0:52:35.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to hide under this desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.25,0:52:39.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What a waste! We wanted to see your reaction too!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.12,0:52:42.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect Shintani to be this surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.32,0:52:44.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next, fifth set-up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.57,0:52:47.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,When Mori-sensei claps his hands, \NHidaka will do some mysterious action
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.50,0:52:50.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I was continuously getting ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.90,0:52:51.87,Marin,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.80,0:52:55.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Did you remember? \NI clapped so hard just now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.77,0:52:56.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.25,0:53:00.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I clapped unusually just now, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.75,0:53:02.07,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.07,0:53:03.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And yet, Hidaka didn't react!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.75,0:53:05.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,You didn't clap hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.70,0:53:07.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I was clapping really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.02,0:53:10.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I also made it obvious like "Hidaka! {\i1}(Clap){\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.55,0:53:18.02,Marin,,0,0,0,,I noticed your cue during the ghost story and did it.\NBut other than that, I didn't remember at all
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.02,0:53:19.12,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I see, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.27,0:53:23.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The one where a girl's voice can be heard, was it played during break time?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.50,0:53:25.65,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,They said it was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.85,0:53:26.95,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.95,0:53:28.17,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You didn't? That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.82,0:53:30.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You wanted to show your reactions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.10,0:53:35.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, you were quite calm. Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.85,0:53:38.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You won't be picked for this anymore, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.05,0:53:42.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,So which is it! Are you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.42,0:53:43.27,Kokona,,0,0,0,,I am glad
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.27,0:53:45.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What is that you're glad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.42,0:53:47.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,But yeah... Oh! Let's move on to the announcements
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.92,0:53:51.10,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We did a lot and went a bit overboard today
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.17,0:53:55.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, please do the announcements
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.87,0:53:57.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Announcements please!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.60,0:54:02.07,Kano,,0,0,0,,Next week, on August 20th,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.07,0:54:06.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin's Ganbare!! FRESH! Monday will be a Maaya special!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.75,0:54:11.45,Marin,,0,0,0,,Solo!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.70,0:54:13.20,Kano,,0,0,0,,Do your best! Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.20,0:54:14.97,Marin,,0,0,0,,It'll be a live broadcast too
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.97,0:54:17.40,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Today's episode was produced by Hidaka
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.40,0:54:18.47,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.47,0:54:19.75,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.75,0:54:20.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.45,0:54:21.25,Kano,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.25,0:54:24.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well of course, that's what we had been talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.10,0:54:26.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Why do you only realize it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.95,0:54:27.85,Kano,,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.85,0:54:30.67,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Next week will be handled by Asou alone
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.17,0:54:33.37,Marin,,0,0,0,,Send her lots of postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.37,0:54:34.37,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.37,0:54:35.37,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Questions perhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.37,0:54:36.65,Kano,,0,0,0,,Or Maaya-related
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.65,0:54:41.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,It'll be like when I did my solo episode with a radio-like set-up
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.02,0:54:44.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Having those postcards will help to motivate her
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.72,0:54:46.07,Kano,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.60,0:54:49.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Since she'll probably be really anxious about this
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.42,0:54:50.32,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,We'll be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.32,0:54:51.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Do your best Asou!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.90,0:54:53.82,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's move on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.82,0:54:54.82,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.32,0:54:58.95,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,On September 7th, "Manners Lesson" will be held!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.27,0:55:05.30,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Yesterday... I forgot her name
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.30,0:55:07.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You did, and what's worse is that she was there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.27,0:55:10.20,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.20,0:55:13.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,We greeted her after the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.67,0:55:15.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Her name was written on a piece of paper here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.80,0:55:17.47,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's the worse manner!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.07,0:55:19.12,Kano,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.12,0:55:20.40,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.40,0:55:21.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I already remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.12,0:55:25.05,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,The lecturer will be Sunai Emi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.15,0:55:29.65,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what we'll be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.65,0:55:31.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,But please look forward to it everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.92,0:55:34.95,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.95,0:55:36.02,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Is there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.17,0:55:41.70,Marin,,0,0,0,,On the same day as the Manners Lesson, this show, Ganbare!! FRESH! Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.35,0:55:47.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,will be broadcasting a pre-recorded video at 9 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.75,0:55:52.35,Marin,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch this too after you finish watching the Manners Lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.35,0:55:54.30,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.27,0:55:54.70,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.70,0:55:57.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Even those that goes to the 3rd period can watch this right after
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.02,0:56:01.35,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to this as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.35,0:56:03.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then- Oh there's more huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.52,0:56:08.77,Kokona,,0,0,0,,Next, it's regarding Sakura Gakuin's Ganbare!! FRESH Monday, 2017 Nendo Outdoor School
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.77,0:56:10.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That's last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.77,0:56:10.77,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,It's 2018!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.72,0:56:13.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,You weren't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.85,0:56:15.30,Marin,,0,0,0,,It's 2018
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.75,0:56:22.57,Kokona,,0,0,0,,It'll be broadcasted in two parts which will be on August 27th \Nand September 3rd so be sure to watch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.57,0:56:24.07,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.15,0:56:27.95,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,FRESH Monday is also having tons of interesting development
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.17,0:56:30.92,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We really went all out today, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.92,0:56:34.00,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Though I do feel like I owe Shintani tons of apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:36.42,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,And of course, towards Fujihira and Nonaka as well
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.60,0:56:38.45,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Let's praise Hidaka for her acting too!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.52,0:56:41.25,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,She was really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.25,0:56:42.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,She's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.17,0:56:44.60,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I believed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.60,0:56:46.40,Kano,,0,0,0,,I honestly believed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.25,0:56:50.47,Kano,,0,0,0,,She was so believable when we were in the dressing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.70,0:56:53.95,Kano,,0,0,0,,When she said her head hurts, I thought she was sick
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.15,0:56:55.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,She has been acting since then
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.77,0:56:58.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,That said, I was walking like this since then as well
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.57,0:57:01.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Too bad there was no one around!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.55,0:57:01.97,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,We didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.55,0:57:04.27,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,How sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.27,0:57:07.05,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's cheer for Asou next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.05,0:57:10.20,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Yes! We'll be watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.20,0:57:12.90,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,I hope she'll succeed! Talk Chairperson!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.90,0:57:13.80,Kano,,0,0,0,,Talk Chairperson!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.80,0:57:15.22,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.37,0:57:18.20,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Now then! Please- Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.20,0:57:21.77,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We're accepting postcards as well! \NThe theme will be "Summer Plan"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.77,0:57:22.92,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Summer plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.92,0:57:25.97,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,We'll appreciate it if you would send them!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.97,0:57:29.55,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Those who have their letters read will be given a sticker
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.82,0:57:32.07,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,What will be shown after this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.47,0:57:37.87,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the outdoor school trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.45,0:57:38.82,Marin,,0,0,0,,I forgot! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.82,0:57:40.52,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Hidaka is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.17,0:57:42.67,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.90,0:57:43.77,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.47,0:57:43.75,Kano,,0,0,0,,Outdoor school!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.07,0:57:47.32,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,The trailer video will be shown so be sure to watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.52,0:57:50.15,Mori-sensei,,0,0,0,,Well then, that's all for today! Day leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.30,0:57:51.20,Marin,,0,0,0,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.05,0:57:52.72,Marin,,0,0,0,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.12,0:57:55.22,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.57,0:57:59.50,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.50,0:58:00.75,Kano,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.47,0:58:02.67,All/Multiple,,0,0,0,,See you next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.67,0:58:03.80,Yuzumi,,0,0,0,,I'm glad everything's fine!
